  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Living in Germany
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Official information for UK nationals moving to and living in Germany, including guidance on residency, healthcare, driving and the Withdrawal Agreement. </p>

  </div>
</div>

